title: #1846 Real Girlfriends in Paris: Basic Beh-bees
description: Bravo has gifted us with Real Girlfriends in Paris, which is about a bunch of basic Americans in...you guessed it. Paris. Brace yourselves for ranch being pulled out of purses.
